                                    <h3 class="project__title"><a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Recipes for the Government</a></h3>
                                    <p class="project__description">Made a web app to emphasize the growth of e-Governance within the country. Used listeners to gather thoughts from people from various social platforms on a particular trend. Processed, categorized and comprehended the data collected using NLP.
