                                    <p class="project__description">Made an app powered by Watson. App converts text, images and speech in foreign languages into user’s native language. It acts as a travel guide and a personal translator.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
								<div class="project">
                                    <h3 class="project__title"><a href="https://innovate.mygov.in/challenges/innovation-challenge-for-developing-new-digital-capabilities-at-the-stations-of-indian-railways/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Indian Railways - Innovation Challenge</a></h3>
                                    <p class="project__description">Proposed a mobile app - "Safar Suhana". Our app focuses on the ease of access and effective reachability to the various railway amenities present in and around the stations. It is going to be an active system that will enrich the passenger’s travel experiences and also aims to bridge the gap between the railways and the passengers travelling onboard.
                                    </p>
